<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Shyne</title>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,300,300italic,400italic,600,600italic,700,700italic,800,800italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans+Condensed:300,300italic,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

<!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
<!--[if lt IE 9]>
  <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
  <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
<![endif]-->

</head>
<body style="background:#e6eff2; padding:50px 0; margin:0;">
<div style=" width:630px; margin:0px auto;">
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style=" background:#00637c url(<%= "#{root_url}assets/email/e_header_bg.png" %>) left top repeat-x; padding:15px 48px 10px 48px; border:1px solid #103140; -webkit-border-radius: 4px 4px 0px 0px; -moz-border-radius: 4px 4px 0px 0px; border-radius: 4px 4px 0px 0px;">
            <tr>
              <td width="28%"><img alt="" src="<%= "#{root_url}assets/logo.png" %>"></td>
              <td width="72%" style="font-family: 'Open Sans Condensed', sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; text-transform:uppercase;">Call with <%= @member.user.first_name %> scheduled for <%= @call_request.scheduled_date %></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style=" background:#fff; padding:32px 49px 15px 49px; border:1px solid #b1c7cc; -webkit-border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px; -moz-border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px; border-radius: 0px 0px 4px 4px;">
            <tr>
              <td width="100%" align="left" valign="top" colspan="2" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px; padding:0px 0px 10px 0px;">Hey <%= @mentor.user.first_name %>,</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td width="100%" align="left" valign="top" colspan="2">

              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td width="100%" align="left" valign="top" colspan="2">
                <p style=" padding:0px; margin:0px; text-transform:uppercase; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px;">Your call with <%= @member.user.first_name %> has been set for <%= @call_request.scheduled_date_short %></p>
                <ul style="list-style-type:none;padding:0px 0px 25px 25px; margin:0px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px;">
                  <li style="padding:10px 0px 10px 0px;font-weight:700;">1. Here’s how to enter the call:</li>
                  <li>A) Dial <%= Phony.normalize(@call_request.twilio_number).phony_formatted(:normalize => :US, :format => :international, :spaces => '-') %> at the scheduled time</li>
                  <li>B) And then enter this Passcode: <%= @call_request.passcode %></li>
                </ul>
                <p style=" margin:0px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px; padding:0px 0px 25px 0px;">That’s it! The member will join the conference call ready to speak. Please be courteous to your customer and make sure to be on-time for the call.</p>
                <p style=" margin:0px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px; padding:0px;">Sincerely,</p>
                <p style=" margin:0px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#474b4c; line-height:21px; padding:0px 0px 25px 0px;">The Shyne Team</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</body>
</html>
